column2: To refresh ref_met speices information of compounds without

select UNIQUE ACC from ref_species right join REF_MET_TO_SPECIES on REF_SPECIES.id = REF_MET_TO_SPECIES.SPECIES_ID left join REF_XREF ON REF_MET_TO_SPECIES.REF_XREF_ID = REF_XREF.ID where species_member IS null and TAXON is not null;
